01:34:56.731 --> 01:34:57.057
" And we take that in the name of Jesus.

01:34:57.057 --> 01:35:00.016
Thank you, Lord.

01:35:00.016 --> 01:35:13.080
Lord, we take the blood and we make much of the blood, and the blood makes much of us.

01:35:13.080 --> 01:35:15.800
It never loses its power.

01:35:15.800 --> 01:35:17.920
Father, I thank you, Lord.

01:35:17.920 --> 01:35:24.600
No hexes, no vexes, no incantations, no voodoo, no satanic anything comes nigh us.

01:35:24.600 --> 01:35:31.110
Every tongue that rises against us, we condemn it.

01:35:31.110 --> 01:35:40.183
We pray for those who despitefully use us and come against us; we forgive them.

01:35:40.183 --> 01:35:43.220
We forgive them, Father.

01:35:43.220 --> 01:35:45.970
We love you, God.

01:35:45.970 --> 01:35:55.513
And Father, we don't take account of a suffered wrong.

01:36:08.040 --> 01:36:21.800
No matter how much they do or what they say or how they treat us, Father, we act in love because God is love and faith works by love.

01:36:21.800 --> 01:36:29.644
And regardless of what we're—we're not moved by what we see, we're not moved by what we feel.

01:36:29.644 --> 01:36:35.182
We're moved by what the word of God says.

01:36:35.182 --> 01:36:40.170
And we thank you, Father, for 1 Corinthians 13.

01:36:40.170 --> 01:36:43.698
Father, we thank you, Lord, for love.

01:36:43.698 --> 01:36:47.360
Love is patient; love is kind.

01:36:47.360 --> 01:36:51.256
We're so thankful for love that you love.

01:36:51.256 --> 01:36:56.760
For God so loved the world that he gave.

01:36:56.760 --> 01:36:59.960
I'm a whosoever.

01:37:02.220 --> 01:37:23.754
And I believe tonight, Father, that we walk in that victory in the name of Jesus, and we have authority over the devil, and we plead the blood, and we hear your voice, and a stranger's voice we will not follow.

01:37:23.754 --> 01:37:37.600
Thank you, Lord, for every single person here tonight, that they have the ability to hear the voice of the Lord.

01:37:37.600 --> 01:37:45.600
For those that are led by the spirit of God are the sons of God and daughters of God.

01:37:45.600 --> 01:37:46.789
I truly believe, and that's what the Bible says: every believer has the ability to hear the voice of the Father.

01:37:46.789 --> 01:37:47.240
You don't need a prophetic voice leading you.

01:37:47.240 --> 01:37:48.079
You have the same Holy Spirit that dwells in the prophet inside of you.

01:37:48.079 --> 01:37:49.035
Yes, there are giftings of the prophetic, but you have the ability to hear God for yourself.

01:38:11.640 --> 01:38:12.011
I believe He dwells in you richly by faith.

01:38:12.011 --> 01:38:48.880
Yes, there are giftings, and God talks to the prophetic, and we can see, but God has given every believer the ability to hear Him.

01:38:49.400 --> 01:38:50.180
Thank You, Lord.

01:39:00.000 --> 01:39:11.335
You didn't leave us defenseless; You gave us Your blood.

01:39:11.335 --> 01:39:35.360
You gave us the Word, the sword of the Spirit, and the shield of faith that quenches all the fiery darts of the wicked.

01:39:35.360 --> 01:39:41.878
We could have been defenseless.

01:39:41.878 --> 01:40:09.147
There's no armor for the backside; it's always to take charge and to take dominion and authority.

01:40:09.147 --> 01:40:44.040
We're not defeated; we're overcomers by the blood of the Lamb and by the word of our testimony.

01:40:44.040 --> 01:40:55.760
We take this blood right now, and we thank You, Father, that You took it all for us.

01:41:04.475 --> 01:41:04.790
You healed every wound, everything about us, in Jesus' name.

01:41:04.790 --> 01:41:06.680
Even our mental health.

01:41:19.695 --> 01:41:21.830
He took that crown of thorns on His head and all that torment that He went through.

01:41:21.840 --> 01:41:28.088
We don't have to be mentally tormented.

01:41:28.088 --> 01:41:41.480
2 Timothy 1:7 says, "God has not given us a spirit of fear, but of power and of love and of a well-balanced mind.

01:41:41.720 --> 01:41:44.227
" I believe that tonight you have a well-balanced mind.

01:41:44.227 --> 01:41:46.267
Jesus took it all for you.

01:41:46.267 --> 01:41:49.300
You don't have to have PTSD.

01:41:49.300 --> 01:42:05.526
You don't have to have sickness and disease in your body or that mental torment—laying in bed at night with the what-ifs of life, thoughts rolling around in your head.

01:42:09.720 --> 01:42:10.260
We take captive our thoughts.

01:42:10.260 --> 01:42:13.400
We use the Word of God.

01:43:22.954 --> 01:43:23.229
You get the Word of God inside of you, and it will change you from the inside out.

01:43:23.229 --> 01:43:30.860
You'll know the truth, and the truth will set you free.

01:43:30.860 --> 01:43:48.090
No psychiatrist, no ChatGPT or whatever trying to counsel people.

01:43:48.780 --> 01:44:10.080
The only thing that's ever going to stick and work in your life is the Word of God.

01:44:27.400 --> 01:44:40.223
The Word of God will change you from the inside out, but you have to understand who you are and read that Bible every single day.

01:44:40.223 --> 01:45:04.204
Father, we take the blood, and we're so grateful for all that You've done; it never loses its power.

01:45:04.204 --> 01:45:14.240
We plead the blood of Jesus, and we thank You, Lord.

01:45:14.240 --> 01:45:16.240
Amen and amen.

01:45:16.240 --> 01:45:25.763
Great is Thy faithfulness.

01:45:25.763 --> 01:45:41.040
Morning by morning, new mercies I see.

01:45:41.040 --> 01:45:46.767
All I have needed, Thy hands have provided.

01:45:46.767 --> 01:46:00.853
Great is Thy faithfulness, Lord, unto me.

01:46:00.853 --> 01:46:08.476
Thank You, Father, that Your faithfulness has overtaken us.

01:46:08.476 --> 01:46:12.307
Surely goodness and mercy follow us, Father.

01:46:12.307 --> 01:46:17.658
We're so grateful for all that You have done for us.

01:46:44.605 --> 01:46:44.920
Oh God my Father, there is no shadow of turning with Thee.

01:46:44.920 --> 01:46:53.960
Thou changest not, Thy compassions, they fail not; as Thou hast been, Thou forever wilt be.

01:46:53.960 --> 01:46:57.343
Great is Thy faithfulness.

01:46:57.343 --> 01:47:00.533
Morning by morning, new mercies I see.

01:47:00.533 --> 01:47:04.587
All I have needed, Thy hands have provided.

01:47:04.587 --> 01:47:12.210
Great is Thy faithfulness, Lord, unto me.

01:47:12.210 --> 01:47:13.680
Father, we're so grateful.

01:47:13.680 --> 01:47:27.493
We jump right in that river tonight and thank You, Lord, that we find what is on Your heart.

01:47:27.493 --> 01:47:58.968
We can go down so many different rabbit trails because of what our flesh thinks we should pray, but I thank You that the Holy Spirit prays through us and we just yield to You.

01:47:58.968 --> 01:48:06.091
Great is Your faithfulness to us.

01:48:06.091 --> 01:48:22.980
A lot of people always ask me, "Brandon, what are you doing when you get quiet?

01:48:25.382 --> 01:48:25.573
" I'm scanning.

01:48:26.147 --> 01:48:31.672
I scan my heart and I'm listening for Him.

01:48:31.672 --> 01:48:34.920
I'm praying silently.

01:48:34.920 --> 01:48:38.245
Is it the President tonight?

01:49:00.196 --> 01:49:00.533
Do You want me to pray over the President?

01:49:00.533 --> 01:49:04.340
Do You want me to pray over Cuba?

01:49:04.340 --> 01:49:07.951
Do You want me to pray over people's health?

01:49:07.951 --> 01:49:13.212
Because last night when I started praying, I had no idea about the people who are brokenhearted.

01:49:13.212 --> 01:49:17.720
51% of over 50,000 people said they'll never go back to church.

01:49:17.720 --> 01:49:33.432
They're hurt and don't want anything to do with it.

01:49:33.432 --> 01:49:40.980
We're talking over twenty-some thousand people just in that little bit of time.

01:49:54.032 --> 01:49:54.624
The poll that Braden's been doing shows where the church is.

01:50:11.945 --> 01:50:18.745
It said many will be offended in the last days; that offense is rising up so much in people's hearts that they don't go to church anymore.

01:50:18.745 --> 01:50:26.870
So the Lord said, "Pray for this.

01:50:26.870 --> 01:50:34.253
" When I saw the heart and it was split, the Lord said, "I'm filling it with liquid love.

01:50:34.253 --> 01:50:41.250
" I didn't know what I was supposed to be praying for last night.

01:50:41.250 --> 01:50:56.627
I was going to pray for President Trump and the decision he is making today, and the Lord said, "Am I leading or are you?

01:51:09.231 --> 01:51:09.507
" I sat there quietly and said, "You are, for sure.

01:51:09.507 --> 01:51:14.920
" He said, "Do I know more than you?

01:51:14.920 --> 01:51:15.720
Yes.

01:51:15.720 --> 01:51:21.920
So don't buck what I'm trying to do here.

01:51:21.920 --> 01:51:22.400
Flow.

01:51:22.400 --> 01:51:31.440
" I thought we should pray for the war, and He's like, "I know more.

01:51:31.440 --> 01:51:38.620
" There are thousands who say, "I'm wounded by the church.

01:51:39.067 --> 01:52:03.420
" The Lord said, "I want you to deal with that hurt inside of so many of these people who have never stepped foot back into a church after the pastor or Sister Clipboard or whoever it was upset them.

01:52:03.420 --> 01:52:19.115
" Maybe a pastor upset you as a teenager, or a girlfriend or boyfriend broke up with you, and you're just hurt.

01:52:19.115 --> 01:52:36.102
The Lord wants to deal with that hurt and wants you to come up higher.

01:52:36.102 --> 01:52:39.280
It's by faith.

01:52:39.280 --> 01:52:48.755
People are just people; they mess up, and we hold them to such a high standard.

01:52:48.755 --> 01:53:15.680
Remember what John Bevere said about holding people to such a high standard, especially people in leadership.

01:53:22.040 --> 01:53:38.740
They're able to hurt us more because we hold them to such high standards versus a waitress at a restaurant.

01:53:38.740 --> 01:53:48.360
If it was anybody else, you'd already forget about it, but you hold them and feel wounded.

01:53:50.285 --> 01:54:19.840
You put people on a pedestal, and the Lord warned us that in these last days it would happen.

01:54:19.840 --> 01:54:34.344
Father, we just thank You that we forgive those who hurt us.

01:54:34.344 --> 01:55:02.740
We thank You, Lord, that these people will go back to church, and when they go, they get a fresh touch from You.

01:55:02.740 --> 01:55:04.888
I've got direction.

01:55:04.888 --> 01:55:11.809
I don't want to move without Him.

01:55:20.955 --> 01:55:21.300
I'm in the Oval Office.

01:55:21.300 --> 01:55:24.949
We pray over President Trump and the decisions.

01:55:36.286 --> 01:55:36.972
I see this white line; it's making his hair glow.

01:55:36.972 --> 01:55:47.200
And I see a white dove falling down on him.

01:55:47.200 --> 01:55:51.800
I see a white dove, the Holy Ghost and fire.

01:55:51.800 --> 01:55:53.853
This is Holy Ghost and fire.

01:55:53.853 --> 01:55:54.271
Hallelujah.

01:55:54.271 --> 01:55:59.036
