01:55:59.036 --> 01:56:04.177
I see an olive branch and it's full of it.

01:56:06.800 --> 01:56:09.982
A light is going to shine on him today as you lift him up.

01:56:09.982 --> 01:56:15.646
As you lift him up, we pray for the heart of the president.

01:56:15.646 --> 01:56:17.891
We pray for his spiritual well-being.

01:56:17.891 --> 01:56:22.255
We pray for his heart that he finds you.

01:56:30.844 --> 01:56:34.208
So what we're going to do, we're going to pray for a revival inside of him, a stirring of the Holy Ghost and fire inside of our president.

01:56:34.208 --> 01:56:39.480
He needs to be refreshed and to have an encounter with the Lord.

01:56:39.480 --> 01:56:45.457
He has a saving knowledge, but now it's time to take it a step further.

01:56:45.457 --> 01:56:52.987
And I see a white glowing and I see his suit—his blue suit comes full of light.

01:56:52.987 --> 01:56:55.200
His tie starts to glow.

01:56:57.600 --> 01:56:58.546
A dove is up there.

01:57:14.867 --> 01:57:15.609
And I saw an olive branch in the dove's mouth.

01:57:15.609 --> 01:57:19.460
Why would that be?

01:57:19.460 --> 01:57:27.370
Was the olive branch representing a dove's mouth?

01:57:49.920 --> 01:57:54.629
I know it says the flood's over, but there's something about this dove flapping his wings over the president.

01:58:12.166 --> 01:58:19.480
I believe a Holy Ghost and fire hitting him; that's a representation a lot of times of the Holy Spirit.

01:58:22.440 --> 01:58:24.232
And there's church bells that are ringing by the dove.

01:58:24.232 --> 01:58:25.976
Two of them.

01:58:25.976 --> 01:58:30.013
Two massive church bells that look like Notre Dame.

01:58:30.013 --> 01:58:30.787
They're brass.

01:58:30.787 --> 01:58:31.560
They're shiny.

01:58:34.448 --> 01:59:03.760
And the bells are ringing across the land and he's calling the people back to church again.

01:59:07.240 --> 01:59:22.030
I see the church bell ringing, giving one more chance across the land.

01:59:22.040 --> 01:59:34.524
We call the president stirred in Jesus' name.

01:59:34.524 --> 01:59:36.996
Stir him up, Lord.

01:59:36.996 --> 01:59:41.690
Father, we call him stirred in the name of Jesus.

01:59:41.690 --> 01:59:46.320
Give him strength, Lord, to finish the job.

01:59:46.320 --> 01:59:52.653
We take authority over the Jezebel spirit that's trying to take down our nation.

01:59:52.653 --> 02:00:19.190
We come against this in the name of Jesus.

02:00:19.190 --> 02:00:23.194
There's a fire on him.

02:00:23.194 --> 02:00:57.790
There's a Holy Ghost and fire at his desk.

02:00:57.800 --> 02:01:04.277
He's at the Resolute Desk.

02:01:19.320 --> 02:01:19.726
I see him.

02:01:19.726 --> 02:01:21.754
He's all alone.

02:01:21.754 --> 02:01:32.180
He's bowed down, and I see a Holy Ghost and fire coming on him.

02:01:39.000 --> 02:01:40.737
I see a light coming on him.

02:01:59.760 --> 02:02:00.354
I see a stirring in him.

02:02:00.354 --> 02:02:05.504
Oh, we thank you, Lord.

02:02:05.504 --> 02:02:14.391
We take authority over that spirit of pride.

02:02:14.391 --> 02:02:21.840
You will not take our president in the name of Jesus.

02:02:21.840 --> 02:02:29.952
We tell you to bow your knee in the name of Jesus.

02:02:29.952 --> 02:03:00.480
We call for a humbling of him as he humbles himself before you.

02:03:00.480 --> 02:04:13.933
Just like he was praying before and he read the scriptures: 'If my people who are called by my name will humble themselves.

02:04:13.933 --> 02:04:18.470
' We humble ourselves before you, Father.

02:04:31.860 --> 02:04:37.393
You said, 'If we would turn away from our wicked ways,' then, Father, we thank you, Lord, that we repent and we turn away from the wicked ways.

02:04:37.393 --> 02:04:50.307
Then you said we would hear from heaven and you would heal our land.

02:04:50.307 --> 02:04:56.382
We thank you, Lord, that you're going to heal the land.

02:04:56.382 --> 02:04:58.196
We call revival once again.

02:05:03.840 --> 02:05:04.072
I see the church bells ringing throughout all the land.

02:05:04.072 --> 02:05:08.598
They're ringing throughout Mexico, South America, Cuba.

02:05:28.720 --> 02:05:29.300
A major revival.

02:05:30.544 --> 02:05:34.347
The bells are ringing in Cuba, Venezuela, and Manaus.

02:05:34.347 --> 02:05:38.200
I'm calling them in.

02:05:38.200 --> 02:05:47.150
Oh Father, all throughout Colombia, Argentina, we're calling in all the lost.

02:05:47.150 --> 02:05:50.345
