02:13:56.480 --> 02:13:56.840
I can have everything my heart desires.

02:13:56.840 --> 02:14:04.600
He gives me my heart's desire: abundance of everything.

02:14:04.895 --> 02:14:25.510
I have health, prosperity, what I need to get the gospel out, healing over your mind, healing over your body, deliverance over you, your marriage coming stronger, debt-free in Jesus' name.

02:14:26.660 --> 02:14:27.230
The fire, the fire.

02:14:27.230 --> 02:14:30.389
Ask me for it.

